<p>The programming logic are as follow. load the medias in album in background thread, and every time, when the medias count % 30 == 0, it will reload the collectionView in main thread.</p>  <p>here is my code</p>  <p>the backgroundThread function</p>  <pre><code>func backgroundThread(delay: Double = 0.0, background: (() -&gt; Void)? = nil, completion: (() -&gt; Void)? = nil) {         dispatch_async(dispatch_get_global_queue(Int(QOS_CLASS_USER_INITIATED.value), 0)) {             if(background != nil){ background!(); }              let popTime = dispatch_time(DISPATCH_TIME_NOW, Int64(delay * Double(NSEC_PER_SEC)))             dispatch_after(popTime, dispatch_get_main_queue()) {                 if(completion != nil){ completion!(); }             }         }     } </code></pre>  <p>the loadMedia functions</p>  <pre><code>func loadMedias() {         Log.shareInstance.p("PTVideo - loadMedias begin", caller: self)         assetLibrary.enumerateGroupsWithTypes(ALAssetsGroupSavedPhotos, usingBlock: { (grp: ALAssetsGroup!, groupBool: UnsafeMutablePointer&lt;ObjCBool&gt;) -&gt; Void in             // do something here             if ALAssetsFilter.allVideos() != nil &amp;&amp; grp != nil {                 if grp != nil {                     grp.enumerateAssetsUsingBlock({ (asset, index, assetBool) -&gt; Void in                          if asset != nil  {                                 self.medias.append(asset!)                             if(count(self.medias) % 30 == 0){                                 dispatch_async(dispatch_get_main_queue(), { () -&gt; Void in                                     self.mediaCollection.reloadData()                                 })                             }                          }                      })                 }             }             }) { (error) -&gt; Void in                 // Handle error                 println("error in fetching assets")         }      } </code></pre>  <p>and calling them in the viewDidLoad function in this way</p>  <pre><code>self.backgroundThread(delay: 0, background: { () -&gt; Void in             self.loadMedias()         }, completion: nil) </code></pre>  <p>everything looks perfect, but when I click on the cell of collectionView, the cell become white as follow... <a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/4WK0Y.jpg" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/4WK0Y.jpg" alt="white cell..."></a></p>